Name: penguin-command
Version: 1.6.11
Release: alt1.qa2

Summary: A clone of the classic Missile Command game
Summary(ru_RU.UTF-8): Клон классической игры Missile Command
License: GPLv2
Group: Games/Arcade
Url: http://www.linux-games.com/penguin-command/index.html
